overview: Of all the stars in the adult galaxy, none has ever shined as bright as Jenna. Now you can see why, one last time. It's Jenna in all her beauty, all her glory and all her incendiary sexuality. Jenna Jameson is a Heartbreaker. And if you ever doubted it, this DVD will put an end to that...
title: Jenna Jameson in Heartbreaker
